reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on June 4, 2020
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very glad to find these!
reviews.reviewText: Buying face masks for protection is not something I ever thought I would be doing. As we start to venture out, I mean we can't stay inside forever, I was looking for something more comfortable than the reusable cloth ones that we have and something that would be disposable after visiting places like the doctor's office. I was very pleased with the price of these and even though they didn't have many reviews, I decided to give them a try. They arrived in just 2 days, much to my surprise. I instantly tried one on and was happy with the fit, overall. They do fit me a little loose, but not too bad. I have a skinny face, so this isn't likely going to be a problem for most people.I decided to do a couple "unscientific" experiments. First, I put it on in the same way I would wear it and I tried to blow out a candle. I tried, and tried and tried. No matter how close I was, I could not even get the flame to move! Okay, that is good, but that mainly protects other people, right? So, I needed to know more. I then went to my sink and gently sprayed water on the outside. It rolled off like a shower curtain! Now that is what I want to see! I am very happy with this purchase. Thank you for making these available.
Great for comfort not sure if it’s actually protecting you since I can see my breath through the mask
